#

Classic Avocado Salsa

10 min
$5
150 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Dietary Tags:

VeganGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Appetizer

Tags:

FreshEasyAppetizer

Description

A fresh and zesty avocado salsa that brings a burst of flavor to any meal!

Ingredients

  • ripe avocados: 2
  • lime juice: 2 tablespoons
  • chopped onions: 1/4 cup
  • diced tomatoes: 1 cup
  • fresh cilantro: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
